      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms mpactR performs filtering for mispicked peaks, inter-sample variation (group), in-source fragmentation, and background noise removal. However, passages do not explicitly name or describe the filter_summary() function, its return structure (named list), or the 'cv' filter. The functional filters (mispicked, group, insource) are confirmed; filter_summary() function signature and cv filter are not explicitly mentioned in provided passages.",
