      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "A technique to determine whether function calls operating on R6 reference objects modify the original data in-place or create independent deep copies. This is critical for metabolomics workflows where unintended mutation of peak tables can silently corrupt downstream analyses.",
